flowPara.flowSpan: OpenStreetMap is a free worldwide map, created by people like you, for the common good. Unlike other map providers, our data is free to download and use

OpenStreetMap is a free, worldwide map maintained by an active community of mappers, and anyone can contribute. OpenStreetMap data powers millions of maps around the world and is free to download and use

OpenStreetMap is a free and editable map of the world maintained by an active community of mappers.
